			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">First, to allow for refresh, cast, and possible fizzle time.
<br />

<br />
Second, sometimes aliases dont perform well without the pause, maybe due to lag.  A very small pause makes sure one command does not activate before it can.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
